Subject: Bitweaver 2.8.1 Multiple Cross-site Scripting Vulnerabilities

Advisory:              	Bitweaver 2.8.1 Multiple Cross-site Scripting Vulnerabilities
Advisory ID:           	SSCHADV2011-021
Author:                	Stefan Schurtz
Affected Software:  	Successfully tested on Bitweaver 2.8.1
Vendor URL:          	http://www.bitweaver.org
Vendor Status:       	informed
CVE-ID:                	-

==========================
Vulnerability Description:
==========================

Bitweaver 2.8.1 is prone to multiple Cross-Site scripting vulernabilities

==================
